npx express-generator StreakTrack --view=ejs

cd StreakTrack

1. Set up MongoDB connection
2. Create User Model
3. Implement Authentication Middleware
4. Create Routes {for user authentication, login, and logout}

npm install mongoose passport passport-local passport-local-mongoose express-session express jquery

